  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A creepy tunnel inhabited by a gigantic creature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped inside this tunnel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The objective of the game is to escape the tunnel by avoiding traps and the giant creature that blocks your progress, while searching for the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short horror game that surrounds the player with a sense of unease and tension.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to play</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's search for the tunnel's exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/f59b60b215736fd1aed09a8cd9e8c86b.poster.avif?t=1745709018\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/f59b60b215736fd1aed09a8cd9e8c86b.webm?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/f59b60b215736fd1aed09a8cd9e8c86b.mp4?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/dbe3fcaf400ff59098cbcb157b917e25.poster.avif?t=1745709018\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/dbe3fcaf400ff59098cbcb157b917e25.webm?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/dbe3fcaf400ff59098cbcb157b917e25.mp4?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are detected and consumed by the giant creature or get caught in a trap, your progress will be reset, and you will be forcibly returned to the starting point.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/3b372f5f1bf16a85f610f38cf0f0b4c5.poster.avif?t=1745709018\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/3b372f5f1bf16a85f610f38cf0f0b4c5.webm?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/3b372f5f1bf16a85f610f38cf0f0b4c5.mp4?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A creepy tunnel inhabited by a gigantic creature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped inside this tunnel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The objective of the game is to escape the tunnel by avoiding traps and the giant creature that blocks your progress, while searching for the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short horror game that surrounds the player with a sense of unease and tension.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to play</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's search for the tunnel's exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/f59b60b215736fd1aed09a8cd9e8c86b.poster.avif?t=1745709018\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/f59b60b215736fd1aed09a8cd9e8c86b.webm?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/f59b60b215736fd1aed09a8cd9e8c86b.mp4?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/dbe3fcaf400ff59098cbcb157b917e25.poster.avif?t=1745709018\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/dbe3fcaf400ff59098cbcb157b917e25.webm?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/dbe3fcaf400ff59098cbcb157b917e25.mp4?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are detected and consumed by the giant creature or get caught in a trap, your progress will be reset, and you will be forcibly returned to the starting point.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/3b372f5f1bf16a85f610f38cf0f0b4c5.poster.avif?t=1745709018\" width=400 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/3b372f5f1bf16a85f610f38cf0f0b4c5.webm?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475730/extras/3b372f5f1bf16a85f610f38cf0f0b4c5.mp4?t=1745709018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
